# Words Sky

## Product

- Treat [UX.md](UX.md) as the rulebook. Core flow: `Landing → Topic → Study → (optional) Map`.
- Copy: Study (not Learn), Map (not Explore), Show translations (not Reveal), Got it (not Next as primary), Still learning (no negative framing), Close (not lone × without label).
- Do not ship [UX.md](UX.md) section 8 out-of-scope items (accounts, streaks/XP, advanced graph editing, pronunciation scoring) without an explicit product decision.

